		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Don't mean to derail the thread, but are you the guy who posted this ad on freelancer?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://m.freelancer.com/projects/gerri_13108878.html">https://m.freelancer.com/projects/gerri_13108878.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />It would help a lot if you could mention the game you want to mod. A few games are very well understood (Mario, Castlevania) and that completely changes how hard the job is.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">add bmps to backgrounds</div><br />Depending on the BMP files you want to add this may very well be impossible. The NES is pretty restrictive.

		

